** 14:07分北上施工便道搶通，道路損傷狀況有待評估。<ref name=x4>{{cite news | language = zh-tw | author = 高公局秘書室 | coauthors =  | url = http://www.freeway.gov.tw/Publish.aspx?cnid=193&p=1954 | title = 「國道3號3.1公里崩塌事件」15：00搶救進度 | work =  | publisher = 交通部國道高速公路局 | pages =  | date = 2010-04-29 | accessdate = 2010-04-29 | archive-date = 2019-06-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190625190141/https://www.freeway.gov.tw/Publish.aspx?cnid=193&p=1954 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| language =zh-tw| author =陳靜萍| coauthors =| url =http://www.cna.com.tw/ShowNews/WebNews_Detail.aspx?Type=FirstNews&ID=201004290022| title =北二高走山  工程便道通了| work =| publisher =中央社新聞| pages =| date =2010-04-29| accessdate =2010-04-29| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160304130135/http://www.cna.com.tw/ShowNews/WebNews_Detail.aspx?Type=FirstNews&ID=201004290022| archivedate =2016-03-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| language =zh-tw| author =| coauthors =| url =http://www.bcc.com.tw/news/newsview.asp?cde=1115578| title =高公局：土方5-6天可清完  道路損傷須評估| work =| publisher =中廣新聞| pages =| date =2010-04-29| accessdate =2010-04-30}}{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>
