** 累計至14時止，清除坍方土石約二十一萬八千九百餘立方公尺。<ref name=x5>{{cite news | language = zh-tw | author = 高公局秘書室 | coauthors =  | url = http://www.freeway.gov.tw/Publish.aspx?cnid=193&p=1970 | title = 「國道3號3.1公里崩塌事件」15：00 搶救進度 | work =  | publisher = 交通部國道高速公路局 | pages =  | date = 2010-05-04 | accessdate = 2010-05-05 | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304082905/http://www.freeway.gov.tw/Publish.aspx?cnid=193&p=1970 | dead-url = no }}</ref>
